=== The Three Stages

    - *Unbearable (Weeks 0)*: Constant severe suffering, considering ending life
    - *Bearable (Weeks 2)*: 50–70% symptom reduction with immediate protocols; difficult but tolerable; can envision continuing
    - *Improving (Months 3–12)*: Fundamental treatments addressing root causes; gradual functional gains; hope restored

